MCP Client for Ollama - Source Building

Building from source:
 dpkg-buildpackage -us -uc

Or using git-buildpackage:
 gbp buildpackage --git-no-sign

The package uses pybuild for building Python packages.
Dependencies are automatically installed from pyproject.toml.

For development, you can also install directly:
 pip install -e .

For more information about the upstream project, see:
https://github.com/jonigl/mcp-client-for-ollama

